---
layout: default
navbar-brand-class: auto-hide
---

.main-content
  .jumbotron
    .container
      %h1
        %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/algolia-logo.svg', class: 'jumbotron-algolia_logo'}
        for
        %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/magento-logo.png', class: 'jumbotron-magento_logo'}

      .row
        .col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3.text-center
          %p As-You-Type Auto-Complete and Instant Search Results Page, all Customizable & Open-Source.

      .latest-version Latest version: <b>{{ site.version }}</b>

      .buttons
        %a.btn.btn-primary{href: 'https://magento.algolia.com'}
          Try it live
        %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-primary-full{href: 'http://www.magentocommerce.com/magento-connect/algolia-search-extension.html'}
          Install the extension now

    .badges
      <iframe src="https://ghbtns.com/github-btn.html?user=algolia&repo=algoliasearch-magento&type=star&count=true" frameborder="0" scrolling="0" width="100px" height="20px"></iframe>
      %img{src: 'https://img.shields.io/badge/magento-1.6.2%2B-blue.svg', :title => "Magento versions supported"}

  .page-section.the-why
    .container
      %h1.headline Build Unique Shopping Experiences
      .row
        .col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2.text-center
          %p With Algolia's as-you-type search customers think less about how to search and more about what they find. Serve relevant content from the first keystroke.

  .page-section.integrate
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-1
          %img.img-responsive.m-l-r-auto{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/ecommerce-search.png'}
        .col-sm-6
          %p <b>Integrate in minutes</b> the Magento default search with Algolia's instant search and increase the conversion rates of your e-commerce site.
          %p Algoliaâ€™s Search Magento Extension makes it easy to deliver a <b>lightning fast search experience</b> to your End-Users.


  .page-section.demos
    .container
      .row.demo
        .col-sm-7
          %img.img-responsive.m-l-r-auto{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/auto-complete.gif'}
        .col-sm-5
          %img.icon{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/autocomplete.png'}
          %h3 Product & Category Autocomplete
          %p Offer End-Users immediate access to your whole catalog from the dropdown menu, whatever your number of categories or attributes.

      .row.demo
        .col-sm-5.text-right
          %img.icon{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/faceted.png'}
          %h3 Instant & Faceted search
          %p Have your search results page, navigation and pagination updated in realtime, after each keystroke.
        .col-sm-7
          %img.img-responsive.m-l-r-auto{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/instant-search.gif'}

  .page-section.features
    .container
      %h1.headline Features
      .row
        .feature.col-sm-5.col-sm-offset-1
          .bubble-outer
            .bubble
              .bubble-inner
                %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/relevant.png'}
          %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/icon-relevance.png'}
          %h3 Relevance
          %p Increase customer satisfaction by serving relevant results. If a user can't find a product, they won't buy it!
        .feature.col-sm-5
          .bubble-outer
            .bubble
              .bubble-inner
                %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/speed.png'}
          %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/icon-speed.png'}
          %h3 Speed
          %p Deliver lightning fast results to your customers, anywhere in the world thanks to our distributed search network.

      .row
        .feature.col-sm-5.col-sm-offset-1
          .bubble-outer
            .bubble
              .bubble-inner
                %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/typos.png'}
          %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/icon-typo-tolerance.png'}
          %h3 Typo Tolerance
          %p Don't let spelling mistakes prevent your users from finding the products they are looking for.
        .feature.col-sm-5
          .bubble-outer
            .bubble
              .bubble-inner
                %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/faceting.png'}
          %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/icon-instant.png'}
          %h3 Instant Faceting
          %p Have your search results page, navigation and pagination updated in realtime, after each keystroke.

      .row
        .feature.col-sm-5.col-sm-offset-1
          .bubble-outer
            .bubble
              .bubble-inner
                %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/analytics.png'}
          %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/icon-analytics.png'}
          %h3 Analytics
          %p From a simple dashboard, get valuable information on how your customers are searching and what they're searching for.
        .feature.col-sm-5
          .bubble-outer
            .bubble
              .bubble-inner
                %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/auto-sync.png'}
          %img{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/icon-sync.png'}
          %h3 Catalog Auto-Sync
          %p Benefit from realtime indexing that instantly captures product additions, price changes, etc. No matter server performance.

      .row
        .col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-4.github
          %i.fa.fa-github
          %h3 Open source
          %p
            Make it look like anything you want!
            %br Open-source, available on <a href="https://github.com/algolia/algoliasearch-magento" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.

  .page-section.showcases
    .container
      %h1.headline Showcase
      .row
        .col-sm-4
          %a.showcase{href: 'http://www.whisky.fr'}
            %img.img-responsive{src: '{{site.baseurl}}/img/showcase-1.png'}
          %br
          %a.showcase-link{href: 'http://www.whisky.fr'} Whisky.fr
        .col-sm-4
          %a.showcase{href: 'http://www.beyondretro.com/'}
            %img.img-responsive{src: 'img/beyond.png'}
          %br
          %a.showcase-link{href: 'http://www.beyondretro.com/'} Beyond Retro
        .col-sm-4
          .showcase.fixme{href: '#'} You?
          %br
          %p.showcase-join Join us!

